											></em
										></span
									><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(244, 242, 242); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"
										><em style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">—</span></em></span
									>
								</section>
								<section style="margin-right: 32px; margin-left: 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"
										><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">卖场信息技术应用现状</span></strong></span
									>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important" />
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">目前来看，全国各主流家居卖场应用信息技术的阶段基本如下：</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">1/ 30%以上的家居卖场连第一阶段</span><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">（信息化阶段）</span
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">都没开始，也就是说卖场是“裸奔”的，除了财务系统不得不用外，其他没有应用任何系统。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">2/ 50%左右卖场进入了第一阶段</span><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">（信息化阶段）</span
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">，除了财务系统外，也上线了一些例如合同管理、收银管理以及行政办公等简单的内部系统。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">3/ 15%左右卖场进入了第二阶段</span><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">（数字化阶段）</span
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">，把内部的系统应用延伸到商户端和消费者端。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">4/ 目前进入第三阶段的卖场<span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">（智能化阶段）</span>，只有和阿里合作后的红星和居然之家才勉强算。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">总体来说，家居卖场的信息技术应用还处于非常初级的阶段，有很大的提升空间。</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">虽然现在很多家居卖场谈数字化营销，利用直播平台+小程序进行线上引流和锁客，但在售中、售后以及商户的服务上，很多家居卖场的数字化应用几乎还是空白。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">相信随着家居卖场间竞争日趋激烈，以及标杆卖场的示范效应，越来越多的卖场会重视卖场整体的数字化建设。</span>
								</section>
