										><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">数字化平台建设路径</span></strong></span
									>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important" />
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important" />
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">我们把家居卖场的系统平台化过程定义为“数字化”平台建设，那么具体应该包括哪些内容呢？</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">首先得梳理清楚卖场、商户以及消费者需要知道哪些数据。</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">1/ 从家居卖场内部经营视角</span></strong
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">来说，卖场需要随时知道这些数据。</span>
								</section>
								<p style="text-align: center"><img class="rich_pages" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="270" data-ratio="0.4670296430732002" data-s="300,640" src="./digitalization/02.png" data-type="png" data-w="1653" style="width: 578px; height: 270px" /></p>
								<p style="text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136)">图 | 商场内部视角需要知道的数据</span><br /></p>
								<p style="text-align: center"><br /></p>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">2/ 从服务消费者视角</span></strong
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">，我们卖场应该随时知道消费者的这些数据，消费者也同样可以知道自己的数据。</span>
								</section>
								<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center"><img class="rich_pages" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="202" data-ratio="0.34966727162734423" data-s="300,640" src="./digitalization/03.png" data-type="png" data-w="1653" style="width: 578px; height: 202px" /></p>
								<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136)">图&nbsp;| 服务消费者视角需要知道的数据</span></p>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span><br />
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">3/ 从服务商户视角</span></strong
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">，我们卖场应该随时知道每个商户的这些数据，商户也同样可以知道自己的数据。</span>
								</section>
								<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center"><img class="rich_pages" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="208" data-ratio="0.3599516031457955" data-s="300,640" src="./digitalization/04.png" data-type="png" data-w="1653" style="width: 578px; height: 208px" /></p>
								<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136)">图&nbsp;|&nbsp;服务商户视角需要知道的数据</span></p>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">作者曾经咨询过很多卖场的管理者，在卖场日常经营中，是否知道上述数据？这些数据对卖场的经营是否重要？</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">得到的答案基本都是这些数据很重要，但的确不知道，得去问相关部门，然后让他们再去收集整理汇总。</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">其中很多数据因为没有系统来支持，是无法获取的。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">比如卖场商户的缴费、欠费情况，需要让财务部门的整理汇总；但卖场的销售数据，如果卖场没有统一收银，没有管商户的订单，也没有上系统，那肯定是无法获得的。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">这就是为什么家居卖场经常被诟病管理粗放、落后，经营能力弱，相比阿里、京东这些线上平台来说，</span
									><strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">我们卖场这样的线下平台掌握的信息太少了，既不掌握商户的销售情况，帮助商户提升销售，也不能掌握消费者的信息，给消费者更好的服务，数字化程度太低了。</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">通过上面对卖场、商户和消费者对数据需求的梳理，可以把家居卖场的数字化平台建设分为三个部分：</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">1、通过搭建消费者口碑服务平台，提升消费者购物体验；</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong
										><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span
									></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">2、通过搭建商户管理服务平台，提升商户经营能力；</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong
										><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span
									></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">3、通过搭建卖场经营数据平台，提升卖场管理水平。</span></strong>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">这些内容对家居卖场来说，都是日常经营中基本的工作内容，但很多卖场由于没有专业的IT人才，管理者对数字化平台的概念也不清楚，所以很难梳理出来，数字化建设也就迟迟没有提上日程。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; min-height: 1em; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">随着红星美凯龙、居然之家、第六空间、大明宫、银座家居等标杆卖场在数字化建设上的不断投入，供其他卖场借鉴的经验也会越来越多。</span>
								</section>
